Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.28,0:00:05.79,Brave-Main,TSUNAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,My lord, you must return.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.79,0:00:07.66,Brave-Main,LORD,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, Tsunamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:10.73,Brave-Main,LORD,0000,0000,0000,,Kojuro will look after the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.98,0:00:15.66,Brave-Main,TSUNAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,But what if Ieyasu's men \Ncome while you're away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.66,0:00:18.99,Brave-Main,LORD,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going because that old man's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.19,0:00:20.85,Brave-Main,LORD,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.64,Brave-Main,LORD,0000,0000,0000,,why is he sending the priestess\Nhe's been hiding back to Izumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:30.17,Brave-Main,LORD,0000,0000,0000,,Sanada Yukimura knows \Nmore than he lets on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.43,0:00:36.13,Brave-Main,TSUNAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,What's so important in Izumo that\Nyou and Sanada are doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.17,0:00:40.36,Brave-Main,LORD,0000,0000,0000,,The Kushimitama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.82,0:00:42.47,Brave-Main,TSUNAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,The Kushimitama?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.47,0:00:46.10,Brave-Main,LORD,0000,0000,0000,,It's a relic that houses \Nthe soul of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.85,0:00:48.48,Brave-Main,TSUNAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,The gods?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:51.35,Brave-Main,LORD,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose someone interested \Nin the popular foreign deities,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.35,0:00:55.07,Brave-Main,LORD,0000,0000,0000,,like Buddha or Kannon, wouldn't\Nknow what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:59.99,Brave-Main,TSUNAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,What do you intend to do \Nwith this soul of the gods?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:04.11,Brave-Main,LORD,0000,0000,0000,,I will acquire it and turn \Nthis world upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.41,0:01:05.79,Brave-Main,TSUNAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,Upside down?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:09.25,Brave-Main,LORD,0000,0000,0000,,I will make the winds of change blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.77,0:01:16.22,Brave-Italic,TSUNAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,My lord seeks to bring \Nmisfortune to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.50,0:01:17.68,Brave-Italic,TSUNAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,He is the...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:21.54,Brave-Italic,TSUNAMOTO,0000,0000,0000,,...Rising Dragon of Oshu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:06.54,Ep-Title,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,The Souls of the Gods
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:09.99,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,That's Izumo Shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.00,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:14.22,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we made it here safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:17.34,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Is there really anything \Nleft down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.64,0:03:19.81,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Burnt to a crisp...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:22.83,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,It looks completely destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:25.01,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:27.95,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:32.96,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,To destroy all of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:36.31,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,They must have been desperate to \Nget their hands on whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:41.81,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up and look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:44.53,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't know what \Nwe're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:48.85,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,Carefully examine anything \Nthat appears suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:49.93,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Isanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:52.48,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Isanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.00,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:57.78,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:00.63,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't run off on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:04.05,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you if something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:09.42,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go look around the perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:11.54,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,You keep an eye on Isanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.99,0:04:13.91,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fire a shot if I find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:18.56,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh. That woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:37.01,Brave-Italic,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,This pillar used to be a beautiful red.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:40.11,Brave-Italic,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,The walls were a brilliant green.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:44.59,Brave-Italic,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It used to be such a colorful \Nand welcoming place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:48.47,Brave-Italic,PRIESTESS,0000,0000,0000,,Isanami, you're so good at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:51.89,Brave-Italic,PRIESTESS,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a great dancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:52.93,Brave-Italic,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Sisters...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:57.03,Brave-Italic,PRIEST,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you will become \NIzumo's best dancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:04:58.40,Brave-Italic,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:05.65,Brave-Italic,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,They're all...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.14,0:05:07.32,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Isanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:10.32,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to go off on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.67,0:05:13.05,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.05,0:05:14.04,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:16.87,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo, why don't you go \Nlook somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:18.13,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:20.00,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You're always saying \Nwe should go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:22.12,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:27.33,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I was actually afraid to see Izumo again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:32.68,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I didn't see it, I still had hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:35.45,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hope that, maybe, someone survived,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:38.15,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,and would be here to greet me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:40.82,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,But it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:43.61,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's all gone, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:47.83,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:50.97,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Wipe your nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:54.50,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,It's filthy, so keep your \Nface hidden for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.51,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.84,0:05:59.58,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:04.44,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,They should be arriving \Nin Izumo about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:07.48,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,Won't they go after Isanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:08.76,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:13.06,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,If you sent her there knowing that, \Nyou must have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:15.22,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,A plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:21.92,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,There must be something in Izumo you needed Isanami to retrieve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.94,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,Is that not what you thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:28.70,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,There are things about Izumo \Nthat only a local would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:32.16,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:38.98,Brave-Main,ROKURO,0000,0000,0000,,I will bring you more tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:45.71,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,However, I do think they might run\Ninto someone along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.22,0:06:52.26,Brave-Main,YUKIMURA,0000,0000,0000,,Who will it be this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:54.99,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Saizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:57.56,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd it have to be Izumo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.01,0:07:02.34,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd it have to be here, \Nand not Kasuga or Ise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:04.94,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to figure that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:07.03,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:11.36,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we can't bring \Nthe dead back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:15.28,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,And you can't pretend it didn't happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.40,0:07:20.29,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,but at least you can figure out why it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:23.71,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,It might not make you feel any better,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:28.38,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,but isn't it the most the living can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.72,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Saizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:38.67,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Get off of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:40.48,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Get off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:45.44,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Just for a little bit! It makes me feel safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.65,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.72,0:07:52.57,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,But if not for this thing we're looking for,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:56.78,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,this place would have been peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:02.70,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Kakei-san's signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:05.88,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Kakei-san, did you find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:07.55,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:10.71,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you'd fire your\Ngun if you found something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:14.22,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I should let you \Nknow I did not find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:15.12,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:19.07,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,I searched everywhere,\Nbut it had all burnt down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.07,0:08:21.14,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,This trip has been worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:25.49,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:27.94,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't this burn down?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.24,0:08:31.62,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,It appears to be made of bronze.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:33.20,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,That must be why it survived the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:36.15,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,It should at least be covered in soot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:42.54,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:46.68,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,This symbol...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:49.51,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:53.76,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,It looks familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:58.84,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see. Hey, let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:01.45,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. It's a yin-yang symbol.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:02.66,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:03.44,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:06.53,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little different \Nfrom the actual symbol.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.14,0:09:07.26,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:09.22,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,There must be some sort of trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.22,0:09:10.23,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.03,0:09:13.47,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we're supposed to \Nmake the correct symbol.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:16.20,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,Can those stones be moved?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.20,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:25.31,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:27.58,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,I am shamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:32.16,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I think it moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:33.20,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,It moves?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:35.01,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:37.61,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,I just tried to move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:42.18,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:48.68,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,...only the center piece moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:53.57,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can I give it a try?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:55.01,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:10.00,Brave-Italic,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,How do I know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:12.67,Brave-Italic,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Have I seen this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:19.34,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:28.69,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:44.11,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:46.87,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,I heard a tall staircase was constructed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:50.97,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,...at Izumo Shrine long ago \Nto reach the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:53.15,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,A stairway to Heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:56.26,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,These stairs seem to be the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:11:00.03,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You mean these stairs \Ngo to the netherworld?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:00.96,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:03.31,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing as Heaven or Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:06.36,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You don't believe in them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:10.75,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I believed we'd be together in the\Nnetherworld even after we died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.75,0:11:13.30,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to live a quiet \Nlife in the other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:16.56,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:23.24,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I think we're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.87,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to be a dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:31.54,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,We came down here for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:34.36,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. There's something written.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:38.30,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:40.28,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's Izumo script.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:42.41,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,Izumo script? Can you read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:43.55,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.87,0:11:47.04,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,It's worthless if we can't read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:51.59,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:53.51,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you've found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:56.79,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,I must thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:59.23,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,Now I don't have to look for it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:00.67,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:01.79,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:05.47,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hand over the Kushimitama.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:08.86,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,The Kushimitama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:14.79,Brave-Italic,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,The Kushimitama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:16.14,Brave-Italic,PRIEST,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:18.72,Brave-Italic,PRIEST,0000,0000,0000,,It's your very own protective charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.13,0:12:20.76,Brave-Italic,PRIEST,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it with you always.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.38,0:12:23.09,Brave-Italic,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Just for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.18,0:12:26.53,Brave-Italic,PRIEST,0000,0000,0000,,You must never remove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:33.23,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're after my hairpin?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:37.11,Brave-Italic,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what they wanted after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:44.98,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't say I was \Nexpecting a hairpin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:47.52,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if you'll hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:49.26,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,We'll never let you have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:51.75,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,If you intend to take it by force, \Nwe accept your challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:55.77,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:57.15,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:00.32,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,What are those lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:03.13,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,They're snakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.30,0:13:06.65,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:07.89,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,No, Kakei-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.72,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,They'll explode if you kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.91,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,What? I can't cut them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:13.85,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,If I could, I would've \Ndone that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.05,0:13:15.59,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,Damn snakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:21.77,Brave-Main,OKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the older one to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:25.36,Brave-Main,OKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Mushikugutsu Hiki Jagyokuken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:28.09,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Kakei-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:33.33,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,My hairpin...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:34.79,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:39.92,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:40.77,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:45.74,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault the priest and sisters...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:49.38,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,If you must interfere with my job,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:53.56,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,just like our meeting at Ueda Castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:55.81,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,I will not hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:59.02,Brave-Italic,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,He's as bloodthirsty as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:02.42,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I... It was my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:04.74,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,No turning back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.00,0:14:24.21,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,Missed by a hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:29.84,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,How long can you avoid my blades?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:39.48,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,G-Get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:41.86,Brave-Main,OKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Your efforts are futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:51.17,Brave-Main,OKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,You're trapped inside my technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:53.98,Brave-Main,OKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,I have all the power here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:14:58.25,Brave-Italic,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,An illusionist?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:02.21,Brave-Main,OKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lick you clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:17.35,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:20.31,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:25.52,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be more of a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:30.02,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,Let's finish this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:35.61,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You want a challenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:38.89,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.89,0:15:42.31,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,You... You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:54.81,Brave-Main,OKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're symmetrical.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:56.76,Brave-Main,OKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,What would you like next?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.04,0:16:00.21,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of your vulgar nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.21,0:16:01.55,Brave-Main,OKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Vulgar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:05.04,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,It is not proper for a \Nwoman to straddle a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:10.19,Brave-Main,OKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing excites me more than\Nbreaking prudish men like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.36,0:16:19.79,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,Ougi Kashozanmai.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:24.71,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:27.23,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.17,0:16:31.22,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:32.51,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:36.43,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anyone else \Nto die for me, Saizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.12,0:16:38.14,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:39.86,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,No one's dying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:45.12,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,I can't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:47.63,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:52.71,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do in that state?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:16:59.49,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.46,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:08.59,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,This wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:19.47,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Who gave you permission \Nto play with my toy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:24.10,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:27.02,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,"My toy?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:34.39,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one allowed to shed blood\N fighting to the death with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:35.21,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:40.58,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,And he's the only one allowed to \Npush me to the edge and kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:42.66,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,Pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:46.40,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna hear that from \Nsome gross, masked bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:52.92,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.73,0:17:56.97,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Behind you, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:11.17,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.17,0:18:13.55,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of you and your swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:16.40,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,You dumb-ass, you just suck at fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:20.37,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,What? Who're you calling a dumb-ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:24.09,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want both \Nof us to die, assist me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.09,0:18:25.93,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,You can't order me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.93,0:18:27.11,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Once we're done with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:30.88,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play with you until \Nyou cry, so come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:33.59,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Until I cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:35.34,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,You're serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:39.79,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:42.69,Brave-Main,OKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,What an unromantic child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:45.88,Brave-Italic,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,I can move.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:50.02,Brave-Italic,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,That wind must have torn her\Nbarrier and broken the illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:19:01.12,Brave-Main,OKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,A hidden gun? That's no fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.91,0:19:09.48,Brave-Main,OKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,I, Okatsu the snake charmer, \Nwill constrict you myself, like a snake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:15.75,Brave-Main,OKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Now you cannot fire your gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:17.78,Brave-Main,OKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:26.47,Brave-Main,OKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,You shot through your own arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:36.29,Brave-Main,OKATSU,0000,0000,0000,,What a strong man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:43.05,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri Kusarigama Ougi Fujinsho!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:19:59.13,Brave-Main,HANZO,0000,0000,0000,,This ends now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:06.57,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Shunko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:12.84,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:21.72,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Your crappy fighting made \Nme waste my energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:22.53,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:25.40,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Your support just sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.22,0:20:30.50,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.11,0:20:33.25,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone got hurt because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:35.47,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,It was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.47,0:20:37.92,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, no one asked \Nthis guy to jump in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:38.95,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:40.21,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:42.85,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,You would've been screwed \Nif I hadn't shown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.85,0:20:43.76,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:46.31,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just glad you are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:52.94,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,It was my fault Izumo was attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.38,0:20:56.79,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't your fault. It was that hairpin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.22,0:21:00.40,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,I did not expect that to be their target.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:04.82,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,My hairpin... The Kushimitama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:07.28,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,So that's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:14.67,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of her! Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:17.63,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Date Masamune!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:22.40,Brave-Main,KAKEI,0000,0000,0000,,Date Masamune? The lord of Oshu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:25.20,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:26.04,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Isanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.05,0:21:28.07,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.07,0:21:30.43,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,Go home and tell your master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.02,0:21:34.39,Brave-Main,MASAMUNE,0000,0000,0000,,I, Masamune, have taken \Nthe Kushimitama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.96,0:21:37.27,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:43.28,Brave-Main,ISANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo! Saizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:49.49,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.24,0:23:23.17,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Saizo, when are we gonna do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.17,0:23:23.91,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.91,0:23:26.73,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You said you'd play\Nwith me until I cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.73,0:23:29.69,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,When are we doing it? I'm ready anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.69,0:23:31.50,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time for that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.50,0:23:33.82,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.82,0:23:35.31,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, recover!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.31,0:23:36.33,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.33,0:23:39.13,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,You'll need all your strength \Nfor a really good fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.13,0:23:41.05,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll go get you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.05,0:23:41.98,Brave-Main,KAMANOSUKE,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.98,0:23:43.98,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that guy? \NHe's so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:46.98,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,The next episode of Brave 10 is\N"The Heart of the Dragon."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:48.83,Brave-Main,SAIZO,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.71,0:23:50.10,Brave-NextEp,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,The Heart of the Dragon
